millennium products group llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Staples
Industry: Distributors - Consumer Staples
Sub-Industry: Food Products Wholesalers
Millennium Products Group, LLC was founded in 2011. The company's line of business includes the wholesale distribution of groceries and related products.




